LEGEND:
R = RESPONSIBLE (Does the work; performs the activity)
A = ACCOUNTABLE (Final authority & approval; "buck stops here")
C = CONSULTED (Provides input; must be heard before decision)
I = INFORMED (Notified of decision; kept in the loop)

IMPORTANT PRINCIPLES:
в”ңв”Җ Each activity should have exactly ONE person marked as ACCOUNTABLE
в”ңв”Җ Usually the "A" person is the leader with most skin in the game
в”ңв”Җ Multiple people can be RESPONSIBLE, but only ONE is truly ACCOUNTABLE
в”ңв”Җ Consult broadly, but have clear decision authority
в”ңв”Җ Communication & transparency via the "I" column is essential
